---
---
<section id="libraries" class="libraries">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="header">
			<h2 class="section-title">Developer <span>Libraries</span></h2>
			<p>Integrate Nostr Mail into your own applications with our ready-to-use SDKs for Flutter and JavaScript.</p>
		</div>
		
		<div class="grid">
			<div class="lib-card">
				<div class="lib-header">
					<div class="icon dart">
						<img src="/dart.svg" alt="Dart Logo" />
					</div>
					<h3>nostr_mail</h3>
				</div>
				<p>A Dart/Flutter package to easily build cross-platform decentralized email clients.</p>
				<div class="tags">
					<span>Flutter</span>
					<span>Dart</span>
				</div>
				<a href="https://pub.dev/packages/nostr_mail" class="lib-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
					View on pub.dev →
				</a>
			</div>
			
			<div class="lib-card">
				<div class="lib-header">
					<div class="icon npm">
						<img src="/npm.svg" alt="npm Logo" />
					</div>
					<h3>nostr-mail</h3>
				</div>
				<p>A TypeScript/JavaScript library for web and Node.js integrations of the Nostr Mail protocol.</p>
				<div class="tags">
					<span>npm</span>
					<span>TypeScript</span>
					<span>Node.js</span>
				</div>
				<a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/nostr-mail" class="lib-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
					View on npm →
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.libraries {
		padding: 100px 0;
		background: var(--bg);
		border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
	}
	.header {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 60px;
	}
	.section-title {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		margin-bottom: 16px;
	}
	.section-title span {
		color: var(--accent-lib);
	}
	.grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
		gap: 32px;
	}
	.lib-card {
		background: var(--card-bg);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		padding: 40px;
		border-radius: 20px;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 20px;
		transition: all 0.2s ease;
	}
	.lib-card:hover {
		border-color: var(--accent-lib);
		transform: translateY(-5px);
	}
	.lib-header {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 16px;
	}
	.icon {
		width: 48px;
		height: 48px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		border-radius: 12px;
		padding: 8px;
	}
	.icon img {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: contain;
	}
	.icon.dart {
		background: rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.1);
		filter: drop-shadow(0 0 8px rgba(0, 188, 212, 0.2));
		color: #00BCD4;
	}
	.icon.npm {
		background: rgba(203, 56, 55, 0.1);
		filter: drop-shadow(0 0 8px rgba(203, 56, 55, 0.2));
		color: #CB3837;
	}
	.icon.dart img {
		/* Apply color to SVG via filter for consistency with our design */
		filter: brightness(0) saturate(100%) invert(56%) sepia(85%) saturate(1514%) hue-rotate(149deg) brightness(98%) contrast(101%);
	}
	.icon.npm img {
		filter: brightness(0) saturate(100%) invert(26%) sepia(91%) saturate(2251%) hue-rotate(339deg) brightness(85%) contrast(98%);
	}
	h3 {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 800;
	}
	.tags {
		display: flex;
		gap: 8px;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}
	.tags span {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		padding: 4px 12px;
		background: var(--border);
		border-radius: 100px;
		color: var(--fg);
	}
	.lib-link {
		margin-top: auto;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: var(--accent-lib);
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 8px;
		transition: opacity 0.2s ease;
	}
	.lib-link:hover {
		opacity: 0.8;
	}
	@media (max-width: 500px) {
		.grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
